# Memory Profiling CLI Options

When editing Python CLIs in `inference_models/profiling/memory`, use `click`
for command-line options.

Format each `@click.option(...)` decorator with every option argument and
keyword parameter on its own line:

```python
@click.option(
    "--batch-size",
    type=click.IntRange(
        min=1,
    ),
    default=1,
    show_default=True,
)
```

Avoid single-line option declarations, even for simple options.
